               <msContents>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; names of the donor; doxology (also with alternating red and black letters, e.g., fols. 24ra, 24vb, 25rb, 26ra, 27ra); groups of lines alternating with black lines on the incipit page of Texts I, II; two lines alternating with black lines in the incipit of Text III; groups of lines alternating with black lines in the incipit of each subsection in Text I; incipit of each subsection in Text II; the word sälam; elements of the punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numerals.</rubric>
                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
                  <!--The data in the items below refers to other items. please remove this items and move the information to the appropriate place.-->
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <note>The miracles in Text II are not numbered.</note>
                  </msItem>
